{"tid":1623130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"對無誠信，無道德底線的政府，黑警仲講獨立調查委員會真係嘥尻氣！","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:03:53.000Z","uid":294333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f21641753045c3e985bf7f5160534bbeffb1dd84","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"五大訴求中嘅，過晒時啦<br />\n對無誠信，無道德底線的政府，黑警仲講獨立調查委員會真係嘥尻氣！<br />\n<br />\n就算有公正法官主持調查，<br />\n邊撚個執行傳召popo證人工作呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為係司法機構執達吏呀？佢哋寄下傳票，貼下法庭公告咋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法官咪又係要警察幫法官執行法庭命令，強制帶證人出庭<br />\n<br />\n好喇，就當係真係有警察作供，你認為popo會有良知講真相咩？出賣同僚篤灰咩？ 無編號搵邊個出庭呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多又係高層，指揮官出席，每日四點高層記招 無限量謊言，死雞撐飯蓋，嘥9撚氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n777奠係槍炮政權，死攬警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話：解散警察，哦，終極攬炒，宣佈進入緊急狀態，實施全國大陸法，老解進場，返屋企摺被瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e42cfb2d5ab62a11f5b196c8b71d7a6a50508fe","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:31:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ef100dc1d4bd525a0aa026f5d5c44d2e50e10d0b","tid":1623130,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:33:20.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"167d90e436f92840f4a731609db674b8e2610d49","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:34:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"72a14e65be4e4a802cd2c16e53929e236aff8fd3","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:37:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7f070f059c6d47542443e193dc49ccb41884a547","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:38:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ecf79b032bfd371949d988cd08f8e4c83bec888c","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2d954778cea3a548d63a2478dba3d07a2e5bb030","tid":1623130,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:03:53.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}